      "dateCreated": "2026-03-20",
      "description": "Reproduces the snMultiome (joint snRNA-seq + scATAC-seq) analysis from 'Epithelial WNT secretion drives niche escape of developing gastric cancer'. Processes 10x Genomics multiome data from wild-type (RZ) and KRAS-mutant (RZK) mouse gastric tissue through QC, MACS2 peak calling, SCTransform integration, clustering, differential expression (MAST), differential accessibility, and JASPAR2020 motif enrichment. Generates Figures 3A-3I and S3A-S3C.",
